      <title>高盛测试家具销售商 Wayfair 的债务需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/goldman-sachs-tests-demand-for-debt-of-furniture-seller-wayfair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，高盛集团正在与杠杆融资投资者举行会议，以了解他们对在线家具零售商 Wayfair 债务的兴趣。]]></description>
